Package: StatsConsort
Type: Package
Title: Streamline CONSORT Flow Diagrams for Clinical Trials
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco
Maintainer: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco <pedrohmp36@gmail.com>
Description: StatsConsort is an R package designed to streamline the creation of
   CONSORT flow diagrams in clinical trials. StatsConsort automates the generation
   of these charts, providing a user-friendly interface that allows for the creation
   of clear and standardized diagrams based on participant recruitment and follow-up data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    magick,
    statebins,
    tibble
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
